<HEADLINE>
FT  03 NOV 93 / International Company News: Malaysia/US deal
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   KUALA LUMPUR
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
MALAYSIAN Helicopter Services has bought a 24.9 per cent stake in US cargo
and passenger charter operator World Airways for USDollars 27.4m, Reuter
reports from Kuala Lumpur.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
